<plot>When he gets to his office after a usual morning of nagging by his wife, Alice (Jane Frazee), Joe McDoakes (George O'Hanlon) starts to daydream about what life would be like married to the beautiful office blonde (Joi Lansing). She, in his dream, turns out to be indolent and parasitical and, when he awakens, life with Alice looks pretty green.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?503835</url></doc>
